item.description:
Dinner and appetizers are available....If ya ever been down for the wed night jam you know the music is good. Well we kicked it up a notch and invited the best of the best to come down and play. Sure to be a great night of music!

Bring your dancing shoes, this will be fun, nominal cover charge.

Look for Neil and meetup table
item.how_to_find_us: meetup table -- - Please look for table with Neil
